data.name: txtTextDateFormats.Text
data.value:
Or construct your own format using: Day: %d - Day of the Month (1-31) %j - Day of the year (1-365/366)
Month: %m - Number (1-12) %b - Abbreviated month %B - Full month
Year: %Y - 4-digit %y - 2-digit
Click 'Help' to see the full list
Examples: %d/%m/%y (24/12/93) %m:%d:%Y (12:24:1993) %Y-%b-%d (1993-Dec-24)
